    40011 [label="LicenseTag (ScopedLicenseTag \"OrtLicenseCategorization\" \"copyleft-strong\" (LicenseTagDescription \"Open source license that requires you to license modifications, as well as any code that ends up in the same binary (including static linking and module modifications), as well as other code that is part of the same work, with the same strong copyleft license. Examples: GPL-2.0, GPL-3.0, AGPL-3.0, EUPL-1.0, EUPL-1.1, EUPL-1.2.\"))"
